  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors have been fully assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels for each factor. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed and documented. Decision: Accepted.",
